{"tid":1745595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(雪雪聲) 促收回林鄭月娥榮譽院士名銜　劍橋大學：無意有任何行動","createTime":"2019-11-22T09:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T22:35:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8db0226f50efbb5e859a841c7fe7011001f1449a","tid":1745595,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"反修例風波持續，上周有三名英國議員去信英國劍橋大學校長、副校長以及沃爾森學院（Wolfson College）院長，要求院校收回香港特首林鄭月娥的榮譽院士名銜，認為她強硬的處事方式觸發香港爆發巨大危機，無理由可繼續擁有榮譽院士名銜。<br />\n<br />\n劍橋大學回覆該三名議員，指學院沒有打算就林鄭的榮譽院士名銜有任何行動，以及表明「我們會避免進一步的公眾評論。」英國保守黨人權委員會成員普爾福德（Luke de Pulford）在twitter張貼劍橋大學的回函時，呼籲香港人去信劍橋大學，解釋林鄭月娥的決策如何危及港人人權，以呼籲校方重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n    So @ProfJaneClarke @WolfsonCam president doesn't want to revoke Carrie Lam's honorary fellowship. Perhaps friends in #HongKong and beyond could write to her *politely* explaining how Lam's decisions have imperilled human rights in their city, and asking her to reconsider. <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/Y11mnhfdnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FY11mnhfdnY&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylhq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=34f42d35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/Y11mnhfdnY</a><br />\n    &mdash; Luke de Pulford (@lukedepulford) 2019年11月21日<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥是學院37名榮譽院士之一，她在2017年5月獲英國劍橋大學沃爾森學院頒授榮譽院士頭銜。<br />\n<br />\n三名英國上議院議員，包括最近為關注香港局勢而成立的國會跨黨派小組（All Party Parliamentary Group，APPG）主席貝內特（Baroness Bennett）、副主席奧爾頓勳爵（Lord Alton）以及自由民主黨上議院外交事務發言人諾貝奧韋爾（Baroness Northover）上周二去信劍橋大學，要求緊急收回林鄭月娥的榮譽院士頭銜。而旅英港人亦在上周六發起於劍橋大學遊行示威，百多名學生、校友及民眾參加，他們敦促校方撤銷林鄭月娥的榮譽院士頭銜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3591233/org/c8da4aa7c5f3c9a859d8bee587c2c6b1.JPG/U_HkBX5I3ZkOGT23hfAGpjMCSNvSepjFYa2kIWGtpCE?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3591233%2Forg%2Fc8da4aa7c5f3c9a859d8bee587c2c6b1.JPG%2FU_HkBX5I3ZkOGT23hfAGpjMCSNvSepjFYa2kIWGtpCE%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=2e0be551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（Luke de Pulford twitter截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/401276/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E4%BF%83%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E6%A6%AE%E8%AD%BD%E9%99%A2%E5%A3%AB%E5%90%8D%E9%8A%9C-%E5%8A%8D%E6%A9%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8-%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7494c3859f12d2a0d261cd42613f4d0bba3a7099","tid":1745595,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78125b65b244dd2920e2966c5f7e1adbb041b9cb","tid":1745595,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:01:22.000Z","msg":"【抗爭者區議會免責宣示】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745587</a>"},{"pid":"05d4600e24b591773bb0ecbecf216fe5ebf0fcc3","tid":1745595,"uid":77092,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"586703f542f9eed5d25038b78cdf5bbd6aa24827","tid":1745595,"uid":49853,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"劍橋應該收唔少大陸人慷慨捐款"},{"pid":"c09afc8dd1454af189493a40304011fdd2fda350","tid":1745595,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:09:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"838ca140b6333fec58f1152f0e2276f1f8a0b377","tid":1745595,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83794a7fa24c36081764e0c9eb122e63ef3b044","tid":1745595,"uid":310446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"究竟係奶到𠽌𠽌聲定係想儲埋儲埋玩鋪勁?<br />\n<br />\n而家先去一去廣告 轉頭返黎同你繼續《極權誘惑》"},{"pid":"928d681564de474e956fcd6cda509955a68c2de0","tid":1745595